body.description: Add storage and style to your space with this floor cabinet featuring a windowpane-style glass door. At just under 14” wide and 12” deep, its small footprint can squeeze into narrow spaces, but is spacious enough to house a variety of items. With its soft-close hinges and interior fixed shelves, this freestanding cabinet is perfect for storing extra hand towels, wash cloths, toilet paper and more. Utilize the open top shelf to display your favorite home decor pieces or a basket filled with extra toiletries, then finish off the look with one of the included two knob choices (polished silver or black). Includes detailed instructions for easy assembly and an adjustable anchor bracket to secure to the wall for added safety and stability. Pair with additional RiverRidge Home Danbury Collection items to add even more stylish storage to your space.
